{"tid":1632462,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傑斯：蘇斯克查的不幸源於哥帥和高普","createTime":"2019-10-06T18:07:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T10:07:01.000Z","uid":137406,"like":33,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"c9a0aff204aa4b411f08e95160880a35ec61818c","tid":1632462,"uid":137406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:07:54.000Z","msg":"曼聯名宿傑斯，認為蘇斯克查要帶領曼聯復興任務艱巨，他需要一段長時間才可以成功，希望紅魔鬼會給予他足夠的時間重建，並謂他遇到高普和哥迪奧拿主宰的時期，實屬不幸。<br />\n<br />\n雖然暫時未有迹象顯示蘇斯克查會有下課可能，不過明顯已被受壓力。傑斯表示：「現時教曼聯真的好困難。蘇斯克查正努力令曼聯復興，他重用年輕球員，希望建造一支有活力的球隊，但他要和高普和哥迪奧拿同處一個時代，真的好不幸。」<br />\n<br />\n「高普已第4季教利物浦，哥帥亦已在這段時間令曼城變得好強，普捷天奴更已第6季教熱刺。所以蘇斯克查都應該有足夠時間重建，他要時間去讓曼聯重新強起來。但最後他會否有這個時間，又是另一回事。」(<a href=\"http://goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoal.com&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEphSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=031a9a2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"9ea30e4ab0e7877fa7acbab7e6903d257567c572","tid":1632462,"uid":52571,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:10:11.000Z","msg":"樓主做一哥好能搶口"},{"pid":"7d76db515a8f9c6618f54e007d5cc01a34606e39","tid":1632462,"uid":13106,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:10:18.000Z","msg":"搵嘢瀨到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ae675ad5e52e43618fa64541a524b68087824a","tid":1632462,"uid":137406,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9ea30e4ab0e7877fa7acbab7e6903d257567c572","tid":1632462,"uid":52571,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:10:11.000Z","msg":"樓主做一哥好能搶口"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:11:06.000Z","msg":"係咪有咩5會"},{"pid":"558ec6e59ea3c09083dfac0c1a2501ab45f28d00","tid":1632462,"uid":36894,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:14:54.000Z","msg":"講到冇鏝猁 獌就排緊榜首咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91214353907da3973012